What's that. Princess?

1029
01:08:59.680 --> 01:09:02.711
- Food.
- That's on my list.

1030
01:09:03.760 --> 01:09:05.879
The TV is out.

1031
01:09:05.880 --> 01:09:08.319
What's that. Princess?

1032
01:09:08.320 --> 01:09:11.159
We need to call a doctor for Mom.

1033
01:09:11.160 --> 01:09:13.064
That's on my list.

1034
01:09:15.040 --> 01:09:17.707
(LOW RUMBLING)

1035
01:09:18.400 --> 01:09:20.079
(HUFFS)

1036
01:09:20.080 --> 01:09:22.906
(INDISTINCT WHISPERING)

1037
01:09:32.920 --> 01:09:34.959
This is stupid.

1038
01:09:34.960 --> 01:09:37.239
I'm gonna tell her we're out of food.

1039
01:09:37.240 --> 01:09:39.861
- But Dad said...
- I don't care what Dad said.

1040
01:09:43.440 --> 01:09:46.983
(TAKING DEEP BREATH)

1041
01:10:04.400 --> 01:10:06.464
(HINGES CREAKING)

1042
01:10:10.800 --> 01:10:12.750
Mom?

1043
01:10:37.920 --> 01:10:39.879
(GASPS. SHRIEKS)

1044
01:10:39.880 --> 01:10:42.387
(GUTTURAL MOANING)

1045
01:10:44.240 --> 01:10:46.144
(SHRIEKING)

1046
01:10:48.480 --> 01:10:50.159
KAYLIE: She needs a doctor!

1047
01:10:50.160 --> 01:10:52.559
You told me she was sick. but she's not...

1048
01:10:52.560 --> 01:10:54.200
You know what your problem is?

1049
01:10:54.226 --> 01:10:55.239
You don't listen!

1050
01:10:55.240 --> 01:10:57.799
I told you not to go into our room. didn't I?

1051
01:10:57.800 --> 01:10:58.612
What do you do?

1052
01:10:58.638 --> 01:10:59.479
You disobey me.

1053
01:10:59.480 --> 01:11:01.199
Why?

1054
01:11:01.200 --> 01:11:04.759
You disobeyed me. so now you get grounded.

1055
01:11:04.760 --> 01:11:07.399
You and your snot-nosed little brother over there

1056
01:11:07.400 --> 01:11:09.759
are not to step foot outside of this house.

1057
01:11:09.760 --> 01:11:11.983
Now. get out of here.

1058
01:11:20.160 --> 01:11:22.189
KAYLIE: OK. Thank you.

1059
01:11:22.520 --> 01:11:24.185
Bye.

1060
01:11:25.600 --> 01:11:27.425
TIM: What did the doctor say?

1061
01:11:29.560 --> 01:11:32.101
He said to have our father call.

1062
01:11:35.440 --> 01:11:37.708
Like the last one.

1063
01:11:39.680 --> 01:11:42.426
Exactly like the last one.

1064
01:11:44.400 --> 01:11:46.464
Same voice.

1065
01:11:55.080 --> 01:11:57.223
(KNOCKING ON DOOR)

1066
01:12:09.720 --> 01:12:11.159
Hi. Bob.

1067
01:12:11.160 --> 01:12:13.359
BOB: I'm really sorry to hear that.

1068
01:12:13.360 --> 01:12:15.119
I hope she gets better soon.

1069
01:12:15.120 --> 01:12:17.319
ALAN: Thanks for that. Bob.

1070
01:12:17.320 --> 01:12:20.759
You know what? I'm just sorry she brought you all the way over here.

1071
01:12:20.760 --> 01:12:26.159
I mean. she's... you know. using her mother's illness to act out.

1072
01:12:26.160 --> 01:12:28.381
Wait till she starts driving.

1073
01:12:28.407 --> 01:12:29.759
This is nothing.

1074
01:12:29.760 --> 01:12:32.279
Well. so sorry to bother you.

1075
01:12:32.280 --> 01:12:34.679
I hope Marie is up and about soon.

1076
01:12:34.680 --> 01:12:36.839
Thank you.

1077
01:12:36.840 --> 01:12:37.701
Hey. you know what?

1078
01:12:37.727 --> 01:12:38.879
Give me a ring next week

1079
01:12:38.880 --> 01:12:41.759
and we'll play the front nine at Arrowhead.

1080
01:12:41.760 --> 01:12:43.799
Great. We'll do it.

1081
01:12:43.800 --> 01:12:45.864
- See ya.
- Take care.

1082
01:13:12.520 --> 01:13:14.279
KAYLIE: Timbo.

1083
01:13:14.280 --> 01:13:18.426
We're gonna have to get really. really brave.

1084
01:13:35.520 --> 01:13:37.584
(TIMER TICKING)

1085
01:13:55.400 --> 01:13:58.670
(PANTING)

1086
01:14:01.200 --> 01:14:03.343
Very clever.

1087
01:14:05.360 --> 01:14:08.664
- Tim!
- (TIMER BUZZING)

1088
01:14:11.840 --> 01:14:14.222
(TIMER CLATTERING)

1089
01:14:16.720 --> 01:14:19.102
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLES)

1090
01:14:19.720 --> 01:14:21.465
(TOY GUN FIRING)

1091
01:14:22.360 --> 01:14:24.822
(EXHALES)

1092
01:14:36.440 --> 01:14:39.550
(LAMP BUZZING)

1093
01:14:50.960 --> 01:14:52.546
Kaylie?

1094
01:14:56.240 --> 01:14:59.159
And we've lost electric.

1095
01:14:59.160 --> 01:15:00.985
Predictable.

1096
01:15:06.320 --> 01:15:08.190
A dead plant.

1097
01:15:47.480 --> 01:15:49.430
It isn't real.

1098
01:16:00.040 --> 01:16:01.599
Daddy?

1099
01:16:01.600 --> 01:16:04.141
(SLOW TYPING)

1100
01:16:05.400 --> 01:16:07.543
Could you fix the lights?

1101
01:16:10.200 --> 01:16:12.039
(TIM SCREAMING)

1102
01:16:12.040 --> 01:16:13.759
(HISSING)

1103
01:16:13.760 --> 01:16:16.711
(PANTING)

1104
01:16:52.800 --> 01:16:55.182
Nice tricks.

1105
01:16:58.840 --> 01:17:00.426
(GASPS)

1106
01:17:01.880 --> 01:17:03.705
MICHAEL'S VOICE: Kaylie...

1107
01:17:06.000 --> 01:17:08.428
(MICHAEL GASPS)

1108
01:17:19.320 --> 01:17:20.860
Oh. my God.

1109
01:17:23.440 --> 01:17:25.265
Do you see him?

1110
01:17:35.160 --> 01:17:35.765
- (PANTING)

1111
01:17:35.791 --> 01:17:36.919
- (KAYLIE SNIFFLES)

1112
01:17:36.920 --> 01:17:39.951
(CELL PHONE RINGING)

1113
01:17:54.640 --> 01:17:56.079
Hello?

1114
01:17:56.080 --> 01:17:58.826
MICHAEL: Just checking in. seeing how everything's going.

1115
01:18:03.160 --> 01:18:04.759
I'm fine.

1116
01:18:04.760 --> 01:18:07.980
OK. I guess I'll talk to you in an hour.

1117
01:18:08.006 --> 01:18:09.454
Enjoyed the chat.

1118
01:18:13.800 --> 01:18:15.829
That's a trick.

1119
01:18:16.960 --> 01:18:18.023
I didn't kill him.

1120
01:18:18.049 --> 01:18:19.026
I couldn't have.

1121
01:18:19.052 --> 01:18:20.679
The plate. it wasn't real.

1122
01:18:20.680 --> 01:18:24.462
I didn't kill him because the plate wasn't real!

1123
01:18:47.800 --> 01:18:50.785
(SOBBING)

1124
01:18:53.800 --> 01:18:55.989
(PHONE CLATTERING)

1125
01:19:02.040 --> 01:19:03.639
Michael.

1126
01:19:03.640 --> 01:19:06.466
What did I do? What did I do?

1127
01:19:11.440 --> 01:19:13.559
TIM: Come on.
We're getting out of here.

1128
01:19:13.560 --> 01:19:14.907
Come on. let's go.

1129
01:19:26.280 --> 01:19:27.519
Hello?

1130
01:19:27.520 --> 01:19:29.529
I need police and an ambulance.

1131
01:19:29.555 --> 01:19:30.655
2705 Hawthorne.

1132
01:19:31.400 --> 01:19:33.679
OK. OK.

1133
01:19:33.680 --> 01:19:35.060
Help is coming.
They'll be here.

1134
01:19:35.086 --> 01:19:36.439
We'll straighten all this out.

1135
01:19:36.440 --> 01:19:39.151
Kaylie. we're OK.

1136
01:19:39.177 --> 01:19:40.770
We're OK.

1137
01:19:41.600 --> 01:19:43.839
Michael. Michael. Michael.

1138
01:19:43.840 --> 01:19:45.559
When was the last time you reset the kitchen timer?

1139
01:19:45.560 --> 01:19:46.226
I don't know.

1140
01:19:46.252 --> 01:19:47.559
Your plan was solid.

1141
01:19:47.560 --> 01:19:49.199
We don't have to do anything.

1142
01:19:49.200 --> 01:19:50.839
All we have to do is just sit here and wait.

1143
01:19:50.840 --> 01:19:52.388
No more than half an hour.

1144
01:19:52.414 --> 01:19:53.519
Your kill switch.

1145
01:19:53.520 --> 01:19:56.079
- You called for help?
- Yeah.

1146
01:19:56.080 --> 01:19:58.064
We're done.
 It's over.

1147
01:19:59.040 --> 01:20:01.559
We get to stand here and watch that thing die.

1148
01:20:01.560 --> 01:20:05.023
(BREATH SHUDDERING)

1149
01:20:24.400 --> 01:20:27.239
It's a trick to get us back inside.

1150
01:20:27.240 --> 01:20:30.305
What if this is a trick to keep us standing there?

1151
01:20:38.320 --> 01:20:40.861
- I called for help.
- Call again.

1152
01:20:45.160 --> 01:20:46.719
MAN: 911. What's your emergency?

1153
01:20:46.720 --> 01:20:48.439
Yeah. hi. I just called.
2705 Hawthorne.

1154
01:20:48.440 --> 01:20:50.359
You're going to have to have your father call.

1155
01:20:50.360 --> 01:20:56.719
The doctor will be there tomorrow.

1156
01:20:56.720 --> 01:20:58.704
(DISTORTED) Timbo...

1157
01:21:00.440 --> 01:21:01.075
KAYLIE: No!

1158
01:21:01.101 --> 01:21:02.369
(PHONE CRUNCHES)

1159
01:21:05.320 --> 01:21:07.429
What do we do?

1160
01:21:09.280 --> 01:21:12.559
We could do nothing. Just wait.

1161
01:21:12.560 --> 01:21:14.319
And watch ourselves get...

1162
01:21:14.320 --> 01:21:17.942
We're gonna have to get really. really brave.

1163
01:21:24.000 --> 01:21:27.270
(INDISTINCT WHISPERING)

1164
01:21:57.840 --> 01:22:00.984
He looked at the mirror and took out a gun.

1165
01:22:06.000 --> 01:22:08.223
We're gonna have to smash it.

1166
01:22:36.720 --> 01:22:38.359
(WHISPERING) That's not real.

1167
01:22:38.360 --> 01:22:40.947
ALAN'S VOICE: I thought I told you not to play around in here.

1168
01:22:41.720 --> 01:22:43.510
It's not real.

1169
01:22:59.280 --> 01:23:01.309
(BOTH YELLING)

1170
01:23:09.240 --> 01:23:10.959
(WHIMPERING)

1171
01:23:10.960 --> 01:23:12.546
Shh!

1172
01:23:25.240 --> 01:23:27.463
(GLASS CRUNCHING)

1173
01:24:03.960 --> 01:24:06.069
(CHAIN RATTLING)

1174
01:24:46.840 --> 01:24:48.824
- Kaylie?
- (GASPS)

1175
01:24:49.520 --> 01:24:51.151
Is he gone?

1176
01:24:54.160 --> 01:24:55.950
He was never here.

1177
01:24:57.640 --> 01:25:00.319
It just herded us upstairs.

1178
01:25:00.320 --> 01:25:02.161
We made the right call outside.

1179
01:25:02.187 --> 01:25:04.359
It's really trying to keep us away.

1180
01:25:04.360 --> 01:25:05.087
It'll try harder.

1181
01:25:05.113 --> 01:25:06.199
We have to get downstairs

1182
01:25:06.200 --> 01:25:07.344
before that anchor swings.

1183
01:25:07.370 --> 01:25:09.279
You have to make sure he's gone first.

1184
01:25:09.280 --> 01:25:12.584
He's gone. I promise. See. he's...

1185
01:25:13.040 --> 01:25:14.466
(SHRIEKS)

1186
01:25:15.000 --> 01:25:16.950
(POUNDING ON DOOR)

1187
01:25:20.960 --> 01:25:22.959
(BOTH WHIMPERING)

1188
01:25:22.960 --> 01:25:25.342
(POUNDING CONTINUES)

1189
01:25:28.120 --> 01:25:31.026
(POUNDING CEASES)

1190
01:25:54.560 --> 01:25:56.703
We've got to get downstairs.

1191
01:25:57.400 --> 01:25:58.959
She's not gone.

1192
01:25:58.960 --> 01:26:00.879
- I'm gonna open the door.
- No!

1193
01:26:00.880 --> 01:26:02.779
I'm gonna open the door.

1194
01:26:02.805 --> 01:26:04.519
If she's not gone...

1195
01:26:04.520 --> 01:26:06.822
I want you to run right down the stairs.

1196
01:26:07.800 --> 01:26:09.209
What are you gonna do?

1197
01:26:09.235 --> 01:26:11.732
Don't worry about that.
Just run.

1198
01:26:16.320 --> 01:26:18.270
You ready?

1199
01:26:19.840 --> 01:26:21.962
I'm gonna open the door.

1200
01:26:21.988 --> 01:26:24.727
You run right down the stairs.

1201
01:26:26.720 --> 01:26:28.988
You trust me. right?

1202
01:26:30.760 --> 01:26:32.824
I trust you.

1203
01:26:37.120 --> 01:26:40.719
One... I love you.

1204
01:26:40.720 --> 01:26:43.944
Two... Straight for the stairs.

1205
01:26:47.000 --> 01:26:48.301
Three.

1206
01:26:51.800 --> 01:26:52.673
- (GRUNTING)

1207
01:26:52.699 --> 01:26:53.934
- (BOTH SHRIEK)

1208
01:27:16.000 --> 01:27:18.507
(GROANING)

1209
01:27:25.160 --> 01:27:27.349
(PANTING)

1210
01:28:05.320 --> 01:28:07.509
(WHISPERING) It's not real.

1211
01:28:16.520 --> 01:28:18.424
Just a trick.

1212
01:28:20.680 --> 01:28:22.630
You're gonna arrest me. Timbo?

1213
01:28:25.320 --> 01:28:26.667
(LOUD GUNSHOT)

1214
01:28:29.880 --> 01:28:31.830
Timbo?

1215
01:28:51.840 --> 01:28:53.505
Tim!

1216
01:28:56.920 --> 01:29:00.429
(FAINT WHISPERING)

1217
01:29:17.960 --> 01:29:19.466
(VOICE SHAKY) Tim?

1218
01:29:31.400 --> 01:29:33.862
(MOUTHING)

1219
01:29:35.880 --> 01:29:37.909
(SCREAMS)

1220
01:29:43.680 --> 01:29:46.267
(CRYING) Mommy. please. no.

1221
