Mommy!

1246
01:30:36.280 --> 01:30:38.025
Come on. Tim!

1247
01:30:38.840 --> 01:30:40.904
(SCREAMS)

1248
01:30:47.320 --> 01:30:49.439
(GASPING SOFTLY)

1249
01:30:49.440 --> 01:30:52.869
(INDISTINCT WHISPERS OVERLAPPING)

1250
01:31:56.080 --> 01:31:59.031
(BOTH GRUNTING)

1251
01:32:10.440 --> 01:32:14.439
It won't let us.

1252
01:32:14.440 --> 01:32:17.346
ALAN: I thought I told you not to play around in here.

1253
01:32:27.560 --> 01:32:28.986
No.

1254
01:32:30.040 --> 01:32:32.104
This isn't you.

1255
01:32:33.000 --> 01:32:34.759
It is me.

1256
01:32:34.760 --> 01:32:35.959
(WHISPERS ECHOING)

1257
01:32:35.960 --> 01:32:38.799
I've met my demons. and they are many.

1258
01:32:38.800 --> 01:32:40.559
WHISPERING VOICE: I've seen...

1259
01:32:40.560 --> 01:32:42.799
I've seen the devil...

1260
01:32:42.800 --> 01:32:44.239
WHISPERING VOICE: And he is...

1261
01:32:44.240 --> 01:32:45.951
and he is me.

1262
01:32:48.720 --> 01:32:50.465
(YELLING)

1263
01:32:52.640 --> 01:32:54.624
Dad!

1264
01:33:00.640 --> 01:33:02.510
Let her go!

1265
01:33:05.160 --> 01:33:07.462
(GASPING)

1266
01:33:43.280 --> 01:33:45.184
Run.

1267
01:33:48.480 --> 01:33:50.703
No! No!

1268
01:33:51.400 --> 01:33:52.799
Daddy!

1269
01:33:52.800 --> 01:33:55.199
(SOBBING)

1270
01:33:55.200 --> 01:33:56.706
Come on.

1271
01:34:01.320 --> 01:34:04.191
(BOTH WHIMPERING)

1272
01:34:09.200 --> 01:34:14.199
(TIMER BUZZING LOUDLY)

1273
01:34:14.200 --> 01:34:16.879
This isn't real! This isn't real!

1274
01:34:16.880 --> 01:34:18.864
This isn't real!

1275
01:34:20.280 --> 01:34:23.345
(BUZZING FADES)

1276
01:34:29.720 --> 01:34:31.749
Kaylie!

1277
01:34:34.000 --> 01:34:35.904
TIM: (DISTANT) Kaylie!

1278
01:34:44.840 --> 01:34:46.949
